data.description: Completely renovated 3 bedroom 2 full bath home located in highly desirable South Buffalo . 1 large bedroom with full bath located on the first floor along with first floor laundry . 2 large bedroom with full bath on second floor. Along with a large center common area which could be used as an office or play area for children. Many areas of this home have original hardwood floors which were re furbished & looking like new. New updates include Kitchen hardwood cabinets, counter top ,Lights & flooring, First floor laundry room, Lower bath has new tub, Vanity, toilet, Tile surround, Tile flooring & lights . Upper bath, new surround, flooring & lights. New engineered Hardwood floors in Kitchen, hall & laundry room. New furnace, interior door. Ceiling fans & much more. Move in ready.
